{"view":"article","slug":"megaminx-f2l-s2l","category":"CHS","subcategory":null,"topDir":"CHS","title":{"zh":"五魔F2L, S2L公式 (第一层, 第二层)"},"content":{"zh":"<p><strong>五魔F2L, S2L公式 (第一层, 第二层)</strong></p><p>本文不包括与三阶魔方 <a href=\"/tutorial/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a> 类似的情况. 在魔方整体转动的意义下，很多 F2L (S2L) 情况都是等价的. 五魔中转动F比三阶魔方更为顺手和常用. 在某些情况下, 块构造比标准的F2L来得方便. 尽可能地减少整体转动. </p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>基态</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/megaminx-f2l-s2l/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/megaminx-f2l-s2l/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/megaminx-f2l-s2l/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/megaminx-f2l-s2l/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' R' / U' R' F R F'\"><strong>R U' R'</strong> / U' R' F R F'</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U R U2' R' / U2 R U2 R'\">U R U2' R' / U2 R U2 R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F R' F' R\"><strong>F R' F' R</strong></span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U' F' U F\">U' F' U F</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U2' R\"><strong>R' U2' R</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R2' U2' R2\"><strong>R2' U2' R2</strong></span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U' R2' U2 R2\">U' R2' U2 R2</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2 R2' U R2\">U2 R2' U R2</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/megaminx-f2l-s2l/zh/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/megaminx-f2l-s2l/zh/image12.svg\" loading=\"l